data.description: Fabulous townhome in a beautiful, gated community, in the Villages at Tule Springs. This Lennar townhome built in 2021 & is ready for move in.  Enjoy the community pool, BBQ pit & picnic area, while minutes away from Tule Springs Regional Park.  SOLAR system installed Nov 2022 covers all sellers utility costs/ NV energy bill $13.00/ buyer to assume this loan. This 4 bedroom 3 bath home has a contemporary feel & open floor plan. Living room adjoins the Chef's kitchen w/custom dark wood, soft close cabinets, oversized island, walk in pantry, SS appliances & lots of ROOM TO COOK!  1/2 bath down.  Upstairs laundry, full bath, 3 bedrooms + Large Primary bedroom w/nice sized walk in closet.  En suite bathroom includes dual sinks, separate shower & Roman tub.  Private backyard is fully landscaped w/pavers, Synthetic grass & BBQ stub.  Washer/dryer/refrigerator/water softener & R/o system all included.  Located near new Park, shopping, schools, hwy access & Nellis / Creech AFB
